<table align='center' width='100%' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'>
		<tr>
			<td colspan='2' bgcolor='c0392b'>
					
					<font face ='times new roman' color='white' size='+3'><big><b>IDEAS FOR PERFECT HOME DECORATION</font></big><br><br></b></td>
			</tr><tr>
					<td>
					<font face ='times new roman' color='' size='+1'><big>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
				<b>	Not all home decorating ideas require a heavy investment of time and money.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp If you're looking for a few affordable home interior decorating ideas to freshen up a room over a weekend, Make your home distinct with these little accents:</b>	</big><br><br></font>
			</td>
		</tr>
			
		<tr>
			<td>
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>Rearrange the furniture:</font><font face ='times new roman' color='grey' size='+2'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pull your furniture away from the walls. Try positioning it at intriguing angles. Arranging the sofa diagonally across the narrow living room will make the room &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;look wider and provide a warm, inviting layout.<br><br></font>
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Paint, paint, and clean: </font><font face ='times new roman' color='grey' size='+2'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You will be surprised by what a coat of new paint or cleaning your existing mouldings and doors will do to any room, or to your entire house. Don't forget baseboards, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;mouldings and doors. Find new colours and useful utensils at your local home improvement store.</font><br><br><br>
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Paint a wall: </font><font face ='times new roman' color='grey' size='+2'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Paint one wall with your favourite colour and make it the focal point. Hang interesting art on that wall and move a nice piece of furniture there.<br><br>
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'> -Bring in plants:</font><font face ='times new roman' color='grey' size='+2'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Greenery always adds a breath of fresh air to a room. If you don't have a green thumb, try silk plants and trees. The quality is so good that it's hard to distinguish them &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;from the real thing.<br><Br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Toss in colour: </font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bright colours and good lighting work together produces instant cheerfulness<br><br>
				
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Ladle on the light:</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; One of the most important things is to have all the natural light you possibly can. People respond very well to light.<br><br>
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Dress up:</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Creative use of mouldings, fabrics, even paint will do magic around your doors and windows. You will find them in wood or synthetic at your home improvement store.<br><br>
					
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Hang pictures or a mirror:</font> Hang pictures that reflect your personality. Try frames that are more ornate. When hanging a mirror, try and position it <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;so that it reflects and nice view or an interestingarchitectural element.<br><br>
			
					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Do not clutter:</font> Clutter always works against you. Keep it simple. Add vertical space with shelves or bookcases in closets or other areas to minimise cluttering as much as possible.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Lay an area rug:</font> An area rug is a wonderful way of defining a conversation area. Try one that complements the room. Lay it at an angle beneath your coffee table.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'> -Group figurines:</font> Pull out your favourite collectibles. Show off your personality. Find a display area and group related objects together, in sets of three or five. Try and vary the shapes.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Add a throw or Afghan:</font> Similar to decorative pillows, throws and Afghans add texture to your furniture. They come in all kinds of natural and man made fabrics. <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Find a pattern and style that you like.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Replace lamps:</font> Lamps are probably the one thing in your home that will give others a clue that your room is outdated. Seek out new and fresh lamps that make a statement.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Add decorative pillows:</font> The good news about decorative pillows is that they are an easy way to add textures and patterns to a room. Still better, they can be changed to jazz up a sofa or chair before your room is ready for a major makeover.</big><br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Add candles/candle holders:</font> This is always a winner. If you have some intriguing candle holders, try those. Use at least two candle holders for balance.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Display a figurine or sculpture:</font> Any eye-catching sculpture or figurine will make a wonderful statement as well as a conversation piece.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'> -Display books:</font> Display a few hardcover books that are interesting and have covers which tie into your decor colour scheme. Preferably, the books should be the larger versions, but should not be too thick.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'> -Display pottery:</font> Earthy and warm, pottery makes a great addition to your interior decor.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'> -Display straw baskets:</font> Similar to pottery, straw baskets add charm and warmth to your home.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>-Use a decorative screen:</font> A decorative screen makes an excellent backdrop in any room. It adds dimension and texture.<br><br>

					<font face ='Arabic Typesetting' color='ec644b' size='+3'>If your room is decoratively challenged, try some of these ideas to add life to your interiors.</font><br><br>

			
			</td>
			</tr>
		
